## Dog Parks üå≥

### Riverside Off-Leash Park

**Wag Score: 9.2/10** ‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê

The crown jewel of our service area. Dogs request this park more than any other destination.

**What Dogs Love:**
- Huge open field (3 acres)
- Excellent mud puddles after rain
- Large dog / small dog separation
- Lots of regulars to sniff
- Water fountain at dog height

**What Dogs Tolerate:**
- Gets crowded on Saturday mornings
- That one aggressive German Shepherd (reported, human contacted)

**Pro Tip:** Morning rides (7-9am) have the best weather and fewer crowds.

